==Publication== The book was released on 22 November 2016.<ref name=TS1>{{cite news | url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2016/09/13/doug-ford-announces-he-is-writing-a-book.html | title=Doug Ford announces he is writing ‘Ford Nation’ book | first=Jennifer | last=Pagliaro | date=13 September 2016 | newspaper=Toronto Star | accessdate=13 September 2016 }}</ref>
