*[[Jonty Hurwitz]] (UK, South Africa)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://phys.org/news/2014-11-science-art-nanosculpture-marvels.html |title=When science and art produce nanosculpture marvels |publisher=Phys.org, Nancy Owano  |date= 18 Nov 2014}}</ref>
*[[Karen Latham]] (US)
